ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"好耐以前有間maiderland做得好好架<br />\n間唔中都會攪下執事cafe 幾好heart<br />\n但執左十世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784003d10222c950e8fc5b7772f2492bfa05457d","tid":98221,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"儲多d錢去日本啦, 香港果d全部臭閪mk黎"},{"pid":"a98b9dd29f4dfe464c135849d39f038539b09dbd","tid":98221,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"Btw 三月兔有冇人去過，我覺得靚果個係果間做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aea38a083df1317d4cd790764f6e678f4a17f8d","tid":98221,"uid":80798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"全香港暫時得六間maid cafe 加三間主題cafe （其實同maid cafe一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n1. A.T. <br />\n香港黎講知名度算第一，早排連日本最出名果個 hitome 都請到黎做一日活動加表演<br />\n但缺點係啲女僕經常只同熟客玩，生客九成放置play你，同埋野食要睇運氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. Moe<br />\n現存歷史最耐，背後有大財團，但地方細，mk妹極多，經常閪面，有得簡唔會去，放置play達八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 三月兔<br />\nMoe 嘅姐妹店，經常亂收費，有傳過做嘅女僕有私下接客，比得起錢嘅可以去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. Maid100%<br />\n場地大，有舞台，但女僕都係只限熟客，同埋會比佢地勁sale合照，你唔買唔洗止意有人理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. little maid<br />\n垃圾，maid唔似maid，唔係閪你面就係自己係到姣個老細，試過坐足半個鐘除左落單同你講兩句野之外就係睇住個老細同女僕係到吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. Dreamy Home <br />\n上手係最女僕嘅女僕cafe <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n自從轉左手之後雖然無乜maid cafe feeling ，但每次去親都有女僕同我傾計玩遊戲，野食係真係由女僕煮比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 糖工廠<br />\n環境舒服，野食出色（不過男人煮）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n缺點係成日太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋收費都偏貴，不過都叫可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. Henshin <br />\n環境大不過好污糟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去過兩次都比人放置play<br />\n唯一優點係坐得耐唔會趕你走<br />\n<br />\n9. 魔法學院<br />\n去過咁多間最好既一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n魔法使會好主動同你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有好多唔同嘅game, 連Sony VR都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地方又夠大又舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n囡囡全部都好得意可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但每次走都要講魔法就有啲煩膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f9c37c1c0bf5083db981dc063eef4ea74bf544","tid":98221,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:41:11.000Z","msg":"魔院上次問都冇問就加鳩我鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb82f07bfb681baf183d86e8ab4880e56702e77","tid":98221,"uid":15883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"啲囡仲難食過啲野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac1104a006f60c0ecab69fff333d827264b2a97","tid":98221,"uid":56935,"like":0,"dislike":0,